Save as public template

 

To save the latest system object dossier as a new template select "Save as public template" action.

In the dialog:

  1. Select Object types... . Choose from the list for which system object the template to be applicable
  2. Enter Template title
  3. Select if the template to be Primary template. If you check the option the template to be applied as a primary template, it will be opened as default template when you create the system object for which this template will be applicable.
  4. Select Template purpose - the template to be applied if the system object is created or when it is uploaded
